"{\"uid\": \"thefrontierpost.com-nadal-says-djokovic-clear-favourite-in-olympics-blockbuster\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS (AFP): Rafael Nadal insists Novak Djokovic will be the favourite when they clash at the Paris Olympics, after the Spaniard battled to victory over Marton Fucsovics in the first round on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9939092745371803, \"rank\": 0.006123566140253898, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 13, \"end\": 25, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 48, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.946706108161082, \"rank\": 0.05482848361611214, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}, {\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal had left his participation in the singles in doubt until the last minute because of a thigh injury, and was made to work hard for his 6-1, 4-6, 6-4 victory.\", \"from\": 201, \"to\": 363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0915806781901947e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old - who has won 14 of his 22 Grand Slam titles on the clay of Roland Garros - believes old rival Djokovic will be favourite when they meet for the 60th time.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999998166131431, \"rank\": 1.8332859744044901e-07, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0314161637214604e-19, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Situations are completely different for him, for me.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's being very competitive.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was not being very competitive for the last two years, so in that case, I think probably he is the clear favourite,\\\" said Nadal, who holds an 8-2 head-to-head advantage over the Serb at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 745, \"end\": 750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0915806781901947e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"score\": 0.9363364117562398, \"rank\": 0.06796617440983077, \"text\": \"Serb\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbs\"}, {\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999998166131431, \"rank\": 1.8332859744044901e-07, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to try my best to bring the best to the court and then let us see how far I can go and how many problems I can create for him.\\\"\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal looked to be cruising after racing through the first set on Court Philippe Chatrier before Fucsovics dug his heels in.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1032, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Philippe Chatrier\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Hungarian world number 83 raised his level after a poor start and forced Nadal to a third set.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1189, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.5697841630073465, \"rank\": 0.6839313673052462, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 1168, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0915806781901947e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fucsovics held three break points for a 3-1 lead in the decider but Nadal withstood the threat, breaking in the following game to wrest the momentum back.\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0915806781901947e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A gritty hold of serve edged Nadal closer to victory, with the Spaniard eventually seeing off a dogged Fucsovics after two hours and 30 minutes.\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0915806781901947e-19, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.946706108161082, \"rank\": 0.05482848361611214, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal, a singles gold medallist at the 2008 Beijing Olympics and doubles champion at Rio four years later, is playing just his seventh tournament of 2024.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9988791956357467, \"rank\": 0.0011220619746046814, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He reached the final in Bastad last weekend but suffered a setback in training on Wednesday, jeopardising his hopes of appearing at a fifth Olympics.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1673, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swedish_Open\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.790685071904417e-36, \"text\": \"Bastad\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swedish_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swedish_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadal teamed up with Carlos Alcaraz in the doubles on Saturday, but he had his right thigh heavily bandaged as the pair won their first-round match in straight sets.\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1821, \"end\": 1835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright \\u00a9 2025.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All right reservedThe Frontier Post\", \"from\": 1985, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": []}]}"